column1: These freely available, derived data sets were produced by J. Alder and S. Hostetler,
US Geological Survey (USGS).  The climate scenarios used are from the NEX-DCP30
dataset, prepared by the Climate Analytics Group and NASA Ames Research Center
using the NASA Earth Exchange, and distributed by the NASA Center for Climate
Simulation (Thrasher et al., AGU Eos Trans, Volume 94, Number 37, 2013,
doi:10.1002/2013EO370002).  No warranty expressed or implied is made by the
USGS regarding the display or utility of the derived data on any other system, or for
general or scientific purposes, nor shall the act of distribution constitute any such
warranty.  The USGS shall not be held liable for improper or incorrect use of the data
Years from 1950-2005 are from the Historical experiment and the years from 2006-2099 are from
either the RCP 4.5 or RCP 8.5 experiments
